        Example:="solve -i ""/home/xieguigang/BLAST/db/MetaCyc/xcc8004/fba.xml"" -o ""/home/xieguigang/Desktop/8004"" -m sbml -f default -d max -knock_out XC_1184,XC_3631")>
    <Argument("-i", Description:="")>
